{"author":{"id":"cff9ab1d2ee9741039b2a60d90cca378a5320ba753398f6f3df8d03abcebee1b"},"ops":[{"type":1,"timestamp":1770886161,"nonce":"pEElKWukmPUsVLBR5LZpPYncLNY=","metadata":{"github-id":"I_kwDORKr0287qSB84","github-url":"https://github.com/bonanzahq/bonanza/issues/45","origin":"github"},"title":"Borrower link shows 'Content missing' due to Turbo Frame mismatch","message":"Clicking a borrower name in /verwaltung shows 'Content missing' instead of navigating to the borrower detail page.\n\n**Root cause:** The borrower name links in _result_item.html.erb are inside \u003cturbo-frame id=\"results\"\u003e (from _search.html.erb:74). Turbo intercepts the click and looks for a matching frame in the borrowers/show response, which has no such frame.\n\n**Fix:** Add data-turbo-frame=\"_top\" to the link in app/views/borrowers/_result_item.html.erb:4 so it performs a full page navigation.\n\n**Affected file:** app/views/borrowers/_result_item.html.erb:4","files":null}]}